    <script language="JavaScript">
        //Código para colocar
        //los indicadores de miles mientras se escribe
        //script por tunait!
        $(document).on('ready', function () {
            setInterval(function () {
                //Consulta de sesión
                                consultarSession();
                            }, 200000);
        });

        function consultarSession() {//Cierra sesion despues de intervalo de tiempo
            $.ajax({
                url: '/ajax/verificar_session.php',
                dataType: 'text',
                success: function (r) {
                    if (r == 'EXIT') {
                        alert('Sesión cerrada.');
                        location.href = '/index.php';
                    }
                }
            })
        }

        function puntitos(donde, caracter) {//Convertir numero en formato moneda a medida que se escribe
            pat = /[\*,\+,\(,\),\?,\,$,\[,\],\^]/;
            valor = donde.value;
            largo = valor.length;
            crtr = true;
            if (isNaN(caracter) || pat.test(caracter) == true) {
                if (pat.test(caracter) == true) {
                    caracter = '\'' + caracter;
                }
                carcter = new RegExp(caracter, "g");
                valor = valor.replace(carcter, "");
                donde.value = valor;
                crtr = false;
            }
            else {
                var nums = new Array();
                cont = 0;
                for (m = 0; m < largo; m++) {
                    if (valor.charAt(m) == "." || valor.charAt(m) == " ") {
                        continue;
                    }
                    else {
                        nums[cont] = valor.charAt(m);
                        cont++;
                    }
                }
            }
            var cad1 = "", cad2 = "", tres = 0;
            if (largo > 3 && crtr == true) {
                for (k = nums.length - 1; k >= 0; k--) {
                    cad1 = nums[k];
                    cad2 = cad1 + cad2;
                    tres++;
                    if ((tres % 3) == 0) {
                        if (k != 0) {
                            cad2 = "." + cad2;
                        }
                    }
                }
                donde.value = cad2;
            }
        }

        function puntitos2(donde, caracter) {//Convertir numero en formato moneda a medida que se escribe
            pat = /[\*,\+,\(,\),\?,\,$,\[,\],\^]/;
            valor = donde.value;
            largo = valor.length;
            crtr = true;
            if (isNaN(caracter) || pat.test(caracter) == true) {
                if (pat.test(caracter) == true) {
                    caracter = '\'' + caracter;
                }
                carcter = new RegExp(caracter, "g");
                valor = valor.replace(carcter, "");
                donde.value = valor;
                crtr = false;
            }
            else {
                var nums = new Array();
                cont = 0;
                for (m = 0; m < largo; m++) {
                    if (valor.charAt(m) == "." || valor.charAt(m) == " ") {
                        continue;
                    }
                    else {
                        nums[cont] = valor.charAt(m);
                        cont++;
                    }
                }
            }
            var cad1 = "", cad2 = "", tres = 0;
            if (largo > 3 && crtr == true) {
                for (k = nums.length - 1; k >= 0; k--) {
                    cad1 = nums[k];
                    cad2 = cad1 + cad2;
                    tres++;
                    if ((tres % 3) == 0) {
                        if (k != 0) {
                            cad2 = "." + cad2;
                        }
                    }
                }
                donde.value = cad2;
            }
            var id = donde.id;//alert(":P "+id);
            var x = id.substring(12);
            if (id == 'txtCuotaRetp' + x + '') {
                var id2 = $("#txtCuotaRet" + x).attr('id');
                var val1 = donde.value;
                var val2 = val1.replace(".", "");
                var val3 = val2.replace(".", "");
                var cuotaRet = $("#txtCuotaRet" + x + "").val(val3);//console.log("x "+x+" id "+id+" valor "+val3+" id2 "+id2+" val "+cuotaRet);
            }
            else {
                x = id.substring(11);
                var id3 = $("#txtVlrGiro" + x + "").attr('id');
                var val1 = donde.value;
                var val2 = val1.replace(".", "");
                var val3 = val2.replace(".", "");
                var vlrGiro = $("#txtVlrGiro" + x + "").val(val3);//console.log("x "+x+" id "+id+" valor "+val3+" id3 "+id3+" val "+vlrGiro);
            }
        }
    </script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/jquery-ui.min.css"><script>
    $(document).on('ready', function () {
        $("#txtDocs").autocomplete({//Autocompletar hoja de vida de cliente con evento de teclados y mouse
            source: "/ajax/ajxconsultarDocProf.php",
            width: 214,
            matchContains: true,
            selectFirst: false,
            select: function (event, ui) {
                var doc = ui.item.value;
                window.location = "/consultaTercero.php?ced=" + doc;
//                console.log("consultaTercero.php?ced="+doc);
            }
        }).on('keyup', function (evento) {
            if (evento.which == 13) {
                var doc = $(this).val();
                //console.log("consultaTercero.php?ced="+doc);
                window.location = "/consultaTercero.php?ced=" + doc;
            }
        });

        $('#txtDocsHuy').keypress(function (e) {
            var key = e.which;
            if(key == 13)
            {
                $('#searchHuy').click();
                return false;
            }
        });
    });

    function consultar_doc2 () {
        var doc = $.trim($('#txtDocsHuy').val());
        if(doc == ''){
            swal("", "Ingrese un número de documento.","warning");
            return false;
        } else {
            window.location = "/suffrige/consultaHuy.php?ced=" + doc;
        }
    }

<script>
    $(document).ready(function () {
        //Navegacion de modales
        $("#openPageslide2").sideNav();
        $(".myBtn1").click(function () {
            $("#noticia_1").modal();
        });
        $(".myBtn6").click(function () {
            $("#noticia_6").modal();
        });
    });

    //Animacion de menu lateral
    (function ($) {
        $.fn.extend({

            sideNav: function () {
                if ($('.pageslideBg').length == 0) {
                    $('<div />').attr('class', 'pageslideBg').appendTo($('body'));
                }
                var $btn = $(this),
                    $pageslide = $($btn.attr("href")),
                    $pageslideBg = $('.pageslideBg'),
                    _width = $pageslide.width();
                $btn.click(function () {
                    $pageslideBg.show();
                    $pageslide.css({'display': 'block'}).animate({'left': 0});
                    return false;
                });
                $pageslideBg.click(function () {
                    $(this).hide();
                    $pageslide.animate({'left': _width * -1 + 'px'}, function () {
                        $(this).hide();
                    });
                    return false;
                });

                return this;
            }

        });
    })(jQuery);

    function showModalMenu() {
        $('#openPageslide2').trigger('click');
    }

    function CloseMenu() {
        $('.pageslideBg').trigger('click');
        $('ul#accordionOr').find(':checkbox').prop('checked', false);

    }

    $(".swipe-area").swipe({//Animacion swipe para cerrar menu
        swipeStatus: function (event, phase, direction, distance, duration, fingers) {
//            if (phase=="move" && direction =="right") {
////                $(".container").addClass("open-sidebar");
//                $('.pageslideBg').show();
//                return false;
//            }
            if (phase == "move" && direction == "left") {
//                $(".container").removeClass("open-sidebar");

                CloseMenu();
//                $('.pageslideBg').hide();

                return false;
            }
        }, allowPageScroll: "vertical"
    });
</script>
<!--<script type="text/javascript" src="/assets/js/ext_html2canvas.js"></script>-->
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function () {
            /* Acordeón para menú */
            var accordionsMenu = $('#accordion .cd-accordion-menu');
            var checkboxes = $('#accordion .has-children').find(':checkbox');
            if ($(this).is(':checked')) {
                checkboxes.prop('checked', true);
            }
            else {
                checkboxes.prop('checked', false);
            }
            if (accordionsMenu.length > 0) {
                accordionsMenu.each(function () {
                    var accordion = $(this);
                    //detect change in the input[type="checkbox"] value
                    accordion.on('change', 'input[type="checkbox"]', function () {
                        var checkbox = $(this);
                        console.log(checkbox.prop('checked'));
                        if (!checkbox.prop('checked')) {
                            checkbox.siblings('ul').slideDown(1000, function () {
                                checkbox.siblings('ul').css('overflow', 'visible !important;');
                                checkbox.siblings('ul').attr('style', 'display:none;');
                            });
                            //checkbox.siblings('ul').css('overflow','visible !important;');
                            //checkbox.siblings('ul').attr('style', 'display:none;').slideDown(500);
                            //
                        }
                        else {
                            checkbox.siblings('ul').slideUp(1000, function () {
                                checkbox.siblings('ul').css('overflow', 'hidden;');
                                checkbox.siblings('ul').attr('style', 'display:block;');
                            });
                            //checkbox.siblings('ul').css('overflow','hidden');
                            //checkbox.siblings('ul').attr('style', 'display:block;').slideUp(500);
                            //
                        }
                        //( checkbox.prop('checked') ) ? checkbox.siblings('ul').attr('style', 'display:none;').slideDown(300) : checkbox.siblings('ul').attr('style', 'display:block;').slideUp(300);
                    });
                });
            }

            /* Opciones de menú lateral Inicio */
            var modulos2 = {
                origin2: {

                },

                },

                    color: '',
                    href: 'tre.php'
                },
                quality2: {
                    color: '',
                    href: 'qu.php'
                },
                call2: {
                    color: '',
                    href: 'listadoLlamadas.php'
                },
                moto2: {
                    color: '',
                    href: 'motos/listado_chequeo.php'
                },
                system2: {
                    color: '',
                    href: 'admin/index.php'
                },
                gestioComercial2: {
                    color: '',
                    href: 'resumen_gestion.php'
                },
                sufinan2: {
                    color: '',
                    href: 'suffrige/cazador_externo.php'
                },
                papeleria2: {
                    color: '',
                    href: 'papeleria.php'
                },
                suganado2: {
                    color: '',
                    href: 'solicitudGanado.php'
                }
            };
            $.ajax({
                url: "/ajax/consultaVista.php",
                type: 'post',
                data: {mod: modulos2, perfil: 3},
                dataType: 'html',
                success: function (e) {
                    var vResult = jQuery.parseJSON(e);
//                console.log(vResult);
                    $.each(vResult, function (a, b) {
                        $('#' + a).attr('href', b.href);
                        if ($('#' + a).attr('href') !== "") {
                            $('#' + a).css('display', 'block');
                        }
//                    console.log(a);
//                    console.log(b.href);
                    });
                }
            });

            /* Módulo Jurídico */
            var aprobCert = [4, 1184, 2533, 2256];
            var adminCert = [2051, 2043, 2355, 2301, 2137, 2189, 1362, 2300, 2302, 1571, 2221, 2032, 2216, 1724, 2218, 1725, 2206, 2090, 1133, 1417, 2215, 2056, 1410, 1135, 61, 1216, 1060, 1378, 3, 4, 1499, 1962, 1482, 1410, 24, 1577, 1210, 1921, 1922, Array, 1362, 1921, 2137, 948, 1378, 2502, 1184, 2533, 2256];
            var userCert = [2502, 2051, 2043, 2355, 2301, 2137, 2189, 1362, 2300, 2302, 1571, 2221, 2032, 2216, 1724, 2218, 1725, 2206, 2090, 1133, 1417, 2215, 2056, 1410, 63, 962, 1210, 1921, 1922, 1482, 1724, 2102, 1410, 1574, 1362, 1482, 1410, 1362, 1921, 2032, 2041, 2044, 2050, 2042, 2051, 2043, 1962, 2045, 1801, 1804, 1854, 1847, 1863, 1947, 1927, 1967, 1984, 2006, 2004, 2011, 2030, 1772, 1802, 1793, 1794, 1795, 1796, 1797, 1215, 2206, 2216, 2189, 2218, 2221, 2301, 2302, 2303, 2300, 2323, 2355, 2322, 1571, 2114, 2466, 2583, 2544, 2379, 2553, 2588, 2650, 2630, 1059, 2483, 2688, 2701, 2837, 1184, 2533, 2256];
            var coordCert = [1083, 1318, 1109, 716, 1340, 1303, 1059, 1244, 1040, 1399, 1012, 1433, 1432, 1055, 1135, 61, 1216, 1060, 1499, 1772, 1793, 1794, 1795, 1796, 1797, 1798, 1799, 1849, 1801, 1802, 1803, 1804, 1814, 2630, 1184, 2533, 2256];

            var ind8 = $.inArray( 2256, auxCert);

                $("#juridico2").attr("href", "/reporte_juridico.php");

            }

            if (ind1 >= 0 || ind2 >= 0 || ind3 >= 0 || 2256 == 1417) {
                if (ind2 >= 0 || ind3 >= 0) $("#juridico2").attr("href", "/certificacionCredito.php");
                if (2256 == 1417
            )
                $("#juridico2").attr("href", "/consultaCertificaciones.php");

            }

            /*  Módulo Gerencial */
            var manager = [715, 769, 1071, 79, 23, 26, 1682, 97, 46, 998, 1808, 1577, 842, 908, 2091, 2090, 3, 4, 1184, 2533, 2256];

            if (ind1 >= 0 || ind2 >= 0 || ind4 >= 0) {

            if (2256 == 1521
        )
            {
                $("#manager2").attr("href", "/stalingrad_view.php");

            /* Módulo Comercial */
            $("#comercial2").attr("href", "/modulo_comercial.php");

<script type="text/javascript">
    /*Funciones par cargar reportes---Deprecado*/
    function Cargar(op) {
        $.ajax({
            url: 'reporte2.php',
            type: 'POST',
            data: {op: op},
            dataType: 'html',
            success: function (r) {
                $('#muestra').html(r);
                $('#cargarReporte').css({"position": "static", "z-index": "0"});
                switch (op) {
                    case 4:
                        CloseMenu();
                        return cargar4();
                        break;
                    case 7:
                        CloseMenu();
                        return cargar7();
                        break;
                    case 8:
                        CloseMenu();
                        return cargar8();
                        break;
                }
            }
        });
    }
    function cargar4() {
        $('#sectionOr').css('display', 'none');
        $('.foot').css('display', 'none');
        $("h2.title-breadcrumbs.title-breadcrumbs--principal#uno").text("Originación");
        $("h2.title-breadcrumbs.title-breadcrumbs--secondary#dos").text("Reporte Diario Desembolso");
        $("#menu-content .faq-list2 a").children().removeClass("item-active");
//        $("#menu-content .faq-list2").children().eq(0).find("span").addClass("item-active");
        var periodoContable = '2020-03-01';
        var fechaDesde = '2020-03-26';
        var fechaHasta = '2020-03-26';
        var oficina = 'todos';
        var coordinador = 'todos';
        var pagaduria = 'todas';

        $.ajax({
            url: 'reporteDiarioDesembolso.php',
            type: 'POST',
            data: {
                periodoContable: periodoContable, fechaDesde: fechaDesde,
                fechaHasta: fechaHasta, oficina: oficina, coordinador: coordinador,
                pagaduria: pagaduria
            },
            dataType: 'html',
            success: function (r) {
                $('#cargarReporte').css({"position": "absolute", "z-index": "10"});
                $('#cargarReporte').html(r);
                $('.tilenews').css('background', '#12A79D');

            },
            beforeSend: function () {
                $('#cargarReporte').html('<center><img src="images/design_loading.gif" \
			   width="140"></center>');
            }
        });
    }
    function cargar7() {
        $('#sectionOr').css('display', 'none');
        $('.foot').css('display', 'none');
        $("h2.title-breadcrumbs.title-breadcrumbs--principal#uno").text("Originación");
        $("h2.title-breadcrumbs.title-breadcrumbs--secondary#dos").text("Reporte de Ventas");
        $("#menu-content .faq-list2 a").children().removeClass("item-active");
//        $("#menu-content .faq-list2").children().eq(0).find("span").addClass("item-active");

        var fechaInformeVenta = '2020-03';
        $.ajax({
            url: 'reporteVentas.php',
            type: 'POST',
            data: {fechaInformeVenta: fechaInformeVenta, tipoReporte: '1'},
            dataType: 'html',
            success: function (r) {
                $('#cargarReporte').html(r);
                $('.titazul').css('background', '#008B81');
                $('.titverde').css('background', '#006D65');
                $('html, body').stop().animate({
                    scrollTop: $('#rVentas').offset().top
                }, 1500, 'easeInOutExpo');
            },
            beforeSend: function () {
                $('#cargarReporte').html('<center><img src="images/design_loading.gif" \
			   width="140"></center>');
            }
        });
    }
    function cargar8() {
        var periodo = '2020-03-01';
        $.ajax({
            url: 'reporte_ventas_semanal.php',
            type: 'POST',
            data: {periodo: periodo},
            dataType: 'html',
            success: function (r) {
                $('#cargarReporte').html(r);
            },
            beforeSend: function () {
                $('#cargarReporte').html('<center><img src="images/design_loading.gif" width="140"></center>');
            }
        })
    }
    function cambioOficina(o) {
        if (o == 'todos') {
            $('#cmbCoord').html('<option value="todos">TODOS</option>');
        } else {
            $.ajax({
                url: 'ajax/coordinadoresOptions.php',
                data: {oficina: o},
                type: 'POST',
                dataType: 'html',
                success: function (r) {
                    $('#cmbCoord').html(r);
                }
            });
        }
    }
    function valida() {
        var com = document.getElementById('comb').value;

        if (com != "") {
            document.getElementById("fDesde").disabled = true;
            document.getElementById("fHasta").disabled = true;
        } else {
            document.getElementById("fDesde").disabled = false;
            document.getElementById("fHasta").disabled = false;
        }
    }
    /*Fin Funciones par cargar reportes---Deprecado*/
</script>

        $('.header-decoration').css('display', 'none');

        $("h2.title-breadcrumbs.title-breadcrumbs--secondary#dos").css('display', 'none');
        $("h2.title-breadcrumbs.title-breadcrumbs--secondary#tres").css('display', 'none');
        $("h2.title-breadcrumbs.title-breadcrumbs--secondary#cuatro").css('display', 'none');

<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="js/source/jquery.fancybox.css?v=2.1.0" media="screen">
<script>
    $(document).ready(function () {
        /*
         *  Simple image gallery. Uses default settings
         */

        $('.fancybox').fancybox();

        /*
         *  Different effects
         */

        // Change title type, overlay closing speed
        $(".fancybox-effects-a").fancybox({
            helpers: {
                title: {
                    type: 'outside'
                },
                overlay: {
                    speedOut: 0
                }
            }
        });

        // Disable opening and closing animations, change title type
        $(".fancybox-effects-b").fancybox({
            openEffect: 'none',
            closeEffect: 'none',
            helpers: {
                title: {
                    type: 'over'
                }
            }
        });

        // Set custom style, close if clicked, change title type and overlay color
        $(".fancybox-effects-c").fancybox({
            wrapCSS: 'fancybox-custom',
            closeClick: true,
            openEffect: 'none',
            helpers: {
                title: {
                    type: 'inside'
                },
                overlay: {
                    css: {
                        'background': 'rgba(238,238,238,0.85)'
                    }
                }
            }
        });

        // Remove padding, set opening and closing animations, close if clicked and disable overlay
        $(".fancybox-effects-d").fancybox({
            padding: 0,
            openEffect: 'elastic',
            openSpeed: 150,
            closeEffect: 'elastic',
            closeSpeed: 150,
            closeClick: true,
            helpers: {
                overlay: null
            }
        });

        /*
         *  Button helper. Disable animations, hide close button, change title type and content
         */

        $('.fancybox-buttons').fancybox({
            openEffect: 'none',
            closeEffect: 'none',
            prevEffect: 'none',
            nextEffect: 'none',
            closeBtn: false,
            helpers: {
                title: {
                    type: 'inside'
                },
                buttons: {}
            },
            afterLoad: function () {
                this.title = 'Image ' + (this.index + 1) + ' of ' + this.group.length + (this.title ? ' - ' + this.title : '');
            }
        });


        /*
         *  Thumbnail helper. Disable animations, hide close button, arrows and slide to next gallery item if clicked
         */

        $('.fancybox-thumbs').fancybox({
            prevEffect: 'none',
            nextEffect: 'none',
            closeBtn: false,
            arrows: false,
            nextClick: true,
            helpers: {
                thumbs: {
                    width: 50,
                    height: 50
                }
            }
        });

        /*
         *  Media helper. Group items, disable animations, hide arrows, enable media and button helpers.
         */
        $('.fancybox-media')
            .attr('rel', 'media-gallery')
            .fancybox({
                openEffect: 'none',
                closeEffect: 'none',
                prevEffect: 'none',
                nextEffect: 'none',
                arrows: false,
                helpers: {
                    media: {},
                    buttons: {}
                }
            });

        /*
         *  Open manually
         */

        $("#fancybox-manual-a").click(function () {
            $.fancybox.open('1_b.jpg');
        });

        $("#fancybox-manual-b").click(function () {
            $.fancybox.open({
                href: 'iframe.html',
                type: 'iframe',
                padding: 5
            });
        });

        $("#fancybox-manual-c").click(function () {
            $.fancybox.open([
                {
                    href: '1_b.jpg',
                    title: 'My title'
                }, {
                    href: '2_b.jpg',
                    title: '2nd title'
                }, {
                    href: '3_b.jpg'
                }
            ], {
                helpers: {
                    thumbs: {
                        width: 75,
                        height: 50
                    }
                }
            });
        });
        $('#motivo2').off('change').on('change', function () {
            var option = $(this).find(':selected').data('id');
            console.log(option);
            $('#rNotificacion').css('display', 'none');
            var my_array = [51,54,56,59,55,49,57,53,52,18,19,16,30,28];
            if (($.inArray(option,my_array)) !== -1){
                $('#rNotificacion').css('display', 'block');
            } else {

            }
        });

    });
    var selected = [];
    function pendiente_datos(id_cred) {
        var idcredito = document.getElementById("id_cred");
        idcredito.value = id_cred;
        $('#boton2').attr('onclick', 'pendiente_credito(' + id_cred + ',26)');
        motivos();
        $("#cont").modal();
    }
    /**
     * Motivos de creditos en pendiente
     * */
    function motivos() {
        var id_pag = 5;
        $.ajax({
            url: 'ajax/motivos_pendiente.php',
            type: 'post',
            data: {id_pag: id_pag},
            dataType: 'text',
            success: function (r) {
                $('#motivo').html(r);

            }
        });
    }

    /**
     * Ver motivo por el cual el credito se encuentra en pendiente
     * */
    function mensaje(id_cred) {
        $.ajax({
            url: 'ajax/confirmar_alerta.php',
            type: 'post',
            data: {id_cred: id_cred},
            dataType: 'text',
            success: function (r) {
                $('#mensajea').text(r);
                $('#mensajea').css("visibility", "visible");
                $('#men').css("visibility", "visible");
            }
        });

    }
    /**
     * ocultar motivo por el cual el credito se encuentra en pendiente
     * */
    function mensajeout() {
        var r = "";
        $('#mensajea').text(r);
        $('#mensajea').css("visibility", "hidden");
        $('#men').css("visibility", "hidden");
    }
    $(document).ready(function () {
        $("h2.title-breadcrumbs.title-breadcrumbs--principal#uno").text("Originación");
        $("h2.title-breadcrumbs.title-breadcrumbs--secondary#dos").text("Formalización");
        $("h2.title-breadcrumbs.title-breadcrumbs--secondary#tres").remove();
        $("h2.title-breadcrumbs.title-breadcrumbs--secondary#cuatro").remove();
        $("#menu-content .faq-list2 a").children().removeClass("item-active");
        $("#menu-content .faq-list2 a[href$='/docsVal2.php']").find("span").addClass("item-active");
        $(".faq-list4 a").removeClass("a-active");
        $(".faq-list4 a[href$='/docsVal2.php']").addClass("a-active");
    });

    function copyToClipboard(elementId, idTr) {
        document.getElementById("message").innerHTML = document.getElementById(idTr).innerHTML;
        var aux = document.createElement("input");
        aux.setAttribute("value", '<table style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10pt;"><tr>' + document.getElementById(idTr).innerHTML + '</tr></table>');
        console.log(document.getElementById(elementId).innerHTML);
        document.body.appendChild(aux);
        aux.select();
        document.execCommand("copy");
        document.body.removeChild(aux);
    }

    function abrirModalUrg(id) {
        $.ajax({
            url: 'ajax/ajxCasaComercialUrg.php',
            type: 'post',
            data: {id_cred: id, op: 1},
            dataType: 'text',
            success: function (r) {
                $("#titleModalUrg").html("Casa Comerciales del Credito " + id);
                $("#bodyModalUrg").html(r);
                $("#modalCertificacionUrg").modal('show');

            }
        });
    }
    function getSelect() {

        var selected = [];
        $('#bodyModalUrg input:checked').each(function () {
            selected.push($(this).attr('name'));
        });

        if (selected.length === 0) {
            swal('Seleccione Casa Comercial')
        } else {
            swal({
                    title: 'Esta Seguro?',
                    text: 'Esta Opciones es irreversible',
                    type: 'warning',
                    showCancelButton: true,
                    confirmButtonColor: '#4cae4c',
                    cancelButtonColor: '#d33',
                    confirmButtonText: 'Si!',
                    closeOnConfirm: false
                },
                function () {
                    $.ajax({
                        url: 'ajax/ajxCasaComercialUrg.php',
                        type: 'post',
                        data: {selected: selected, op: 2},
                        dataType: 'text',
                        success: function (r) {
                            location.reload();
                        }
                    });

                });
        }
    }
    /**
     * Funcion para abrir modal para enviar a AL COORDINADOR
     * */

    function pendiente_datos2(id_cred) {
        var idcredito = document.getElementById("id_cred");
        idcredito.value = id_cred;
        motivos();
        $("#coordinador").modal();
    }
    /**
     * Funcion para enviar a AL COORDINADOR
     */
    function regresar_coordinador() {

        var id_cred = document.getElementById("id_cred").value;
        var descripcion = document.getElementById("area2").value;
        var motivo = document.getElementById("motivo2").value;
        var estado_id = 36;

        var conformidad = $('#notificacion').prop('checked');

        if (descripcion != '') {
            $.ajax({
                url: 'ajax/regresar_coord_conf.php',
                data: {id_credito: id_cred, motivo: motivo, descripcion: descripcion, estado_id: estado_id, estado_nom: 'DEVOLUCION_APROBADO'},
                dataType: 'text',
                type: 'post',
                success: function (r) {
                    if (r == 'CRÉDITO REGRESADO') {
                        if(conformidad){
                            $.ajax({
                                url: 'ajax/ajxNoConformidad.php',
                                data:{motivo: $("#motivo").val(), comentario: $("#area2").val(), notif: '0', credito_id: id_cred,
                                    estado: 3, motivo_detalle:'', op: 3},
                                dataType: 'text',
                                type: 'POST',
                                success: function (r) {
                                    swal({
                                        title: "",
                                        text: "Devuelto correctamente",
                                        type: "success"
                                    }, function () {
                                        location.reload();
                                    });
                                }
                            });
                        } else {
                            swal({
                                title: "",
                                text: "Devuelto correctamente",
                                type: "success"
                            }, function () {
                                location.reload();
                            });
                        }


                    } else {
                        swal("", r, "error");
                    }
                }
            });
        }
    }
</script>

<script> 
    $(document).ready(function() {
        // Show or hide the sticky footer button
        $(window).scroll(function() {
            if ($(this).scrollTop() > 200) {
                $('.go-top').fadeIn(200);
            } else {
                $('.go-top').fadeOut(200);
            }
        });

        // Animate the scroll to top
        $('.go-top').click(function(event) {
            event.preventDefault();

            $('html, body').animate({scrollTop: 0}, 300);
        })
    });
</script>
